# Generated installers — never commit binaries to git.
# Installers are published as GitHub Release assets (softprops/action-gh-release),
# not stored in the repo. Tracking a 5+ MB .exe in git history bloats clones
# and there's no integrity check or signature on a committed binary anyway.
*.exe
*.msi

